{
  "texts": [
    "Chatbots are low-cost communication tools developed for effective, intelligent, customized conversations between humans and machines [12].",
    "Chatbots are already prevalent and wellknown to users in several sectors [13][14][15], such as finance (banks), medical, education, administration, and marketing.",
    "Generative AI (GenAI), an AI field specialized in data generation [16], contributes highly to chatbot design and creation.",
    "One very powerful generative AI chatbot built on large language models (LLM) is the OpenAI ChatGPT [17,18].",
    "ChatGPT is currently utilized in several fields [19,20] for its ability to effectively respond to diverse queries by generating texts, videos, or images depending on the requests."
  ]
}